Omotola Jalade Ekeinde mụrụ Omotola Jalade, (amuru 7 Febuwari 1978) bu Onye omee Naijiria Kemgbe ihe nkiri Nollywood mere mpụta mbụ na 1995, Omotola apụtala na ihe nkiri 300, na-ere ọtụtụ nde ihe nkiri a na akpọ vidio

ka ha nwetasịrị ọtụtụ ihe nrite dị elu, malite ọrụ egwu, na ịkpakọba ndị na-akwado ndị na-anụ ọkụ n'obi, ndị nta akụkọ akpọwo ya dị ka ezigbo Afrika Magic.Omotola bụ onye mbụ ama ama n'Afrịka nwetara mmasị karịrị otu nde na ibe Facebook ya. Ugbu a ọ nwere ngụkọta nke nde mmadụ atọ na-eso ụzọ na Facebook.
Omotola Jalade, onye sitere na Ondo, amuru na Lagos State
Omotola tolitere na ezinụlọ mmadụ ise: nne na nna ya na ụmụnne ya nwoke abụọ; Tayo na Bolaji Jalade
Nne ya, Oluwatoyin Jalade née Amori Oguntade, rụrụ ọrụ na JT Chanrai Nigeria, na nna ya, Oluwashola Jalade, rụrụ ọrụ na YMCA na Lagos Country Club
Ebumnobi Omotola na mbụ bụ ịrụ ọrụ na njikwa azụmaahịa, ebe ọ na-eche nsonaazụ ya na mahadum, ọ malitere ime ihe ngosi iji kpata ego
Omotola Jalade gara ụlọ akwụkwọ Chrisland, Opebi (1981-1987), Oxford Children School (1987), Santos Layout, na Command Secondary School  (1988-1993)
O nwere obere oge na Mahadum Obafemi Awolowo wee gụchaa akwụkwọ na Yaba College of Technology (1996-2004), ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ nchịkwa ụlọ
Akpọbatara Omotola Jalade ka ọ na-eme ihe nkiri site n'iso otu enyi ya gaa ebe nkiri
Ọrụ izizi ya bụ na ihe nkiri 1995 Venom of Justice, nke Reginald Ebere duziri
Akpọrọla Reginald ka ọ malitere ọrụ Omotola
Enyere ya onye isi n'ihe nkiri ahụ, bụ nke mere ka ọ rụọ ọrụ na-aga nke ọma na ụlọ ọrụ ihe nkiri Nollywood
Omotola Jalade nwetara nnukwu ọrụ mbụ ya na ihe nkiri ama ama nke Mortal Inheritance (1995)
N'ime ihe nkiri ahụ, ọ gosiputara dị ka onye ọrịa sickle cell bụ́ onye lụrụ ọgụ maka ndụ ya n'agbanyeghị na ọ ga-adị ndụ
Àgwà Omotola meriri ọrịa ahụ wee mụọ nwa
A na-ewere ihe nkiri a dị ka otu n'ime ihe nkiri kacha mma nke Naijiria mere
Kemgbe ahụ, ọ na-egwuri egwu na ọtụtụ ihe nkiri blockbuster, gụnyere Games Women Play, Blood Sisters, All My Life, My Story, The Woman in Me na ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ.

Mgbe ọ rụchara ọrụ na-akọwapụta ọrụ na ihe nketa nke Mortal, ihe ngosi Omotola meriri ya "Onye na-eme ihe nkiri kachasị mma na ihe nkiri Bekee na-ekwu okwu" na "Onye na-eme ihe nkiri n'ozuzu" na (1997) Movie Awards
Ọ bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri kacha nta na Naijiria n'oge ahụ iji nweta ọkwa a

N'ọgwụgwụ 1990s na mmalite 2000s, onye na-eme ihe nkiri a ma ama na-eme ihe nkiri n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri na-esote, gụnyere Lost Kingdom II, Kosorogun II, na Blood Sister II, na-eduga na nnukwu ihe mmeri n'aha Global Excellence Recognition Awards na afọ (2004)
Ka ọ na-erule etiti afọ (2000), Omotola abanyela n'ọkwa ndepụta "A"
Enyere ya onye na-eme ihe nkiri kacha mma n'ọrụ nkwado n'oge ihe nkiri African Movie Academy Awards na (2005)
Mgbe ọ gbasịrị ihe nkiri vidiyo ihe dị ka narị atọ (300), Omotola Jalade nwetara ọrụ nkiri sinima mbụ ya n'afọ (2010) ihe nkiri "Ije"
A gbara ihe nkiri a n'ebe dị na Jos na United States
"Ije" bụ ihe nkiri Nollywood kacha enweta ego n'oge ahụ - A mechara kuchapu site na Phone Swap (2012)

Na ọ gosiputara na Nollywood blockbuster thriller: Last Flight to Abuja nke meriri Hollywood blockbusters dị ka Spiderman, Chee echiche dị ka nwoke, Ice Age, The Avengers, na Madagascar to be 2nd most-grossing movies in West African cinemas in (2012)
Omotola Jalade gara n'ihu inweta ihe nrite iri anọ (40) nke ụlọ na mba ụwa
A na-ewere ya dị ka onye na-eme ihe nkiri kachasị na igbe ụlọ ọrụ Africa
N'afọ 2015, Omotola Jalade mere emume ncheta afọ iri abụọ ya na ụlọ ọrụ ntụrụndụ
